      "Interrogative Pronouns"
    ]
  ],
  [
    "article",
    {},
    [
      "section",
      {},
      [
        "p",
        {},
        "Interrogative pronouns are used to ask questions. In Greek, almost\n            all interrogative pronouns carry an accent mark to distinguish them\n            from their non-interrogative counterparts."
      ],
      [
        "div",
        {
          "className": "interrogative-grid mt-8"
        },
        [
          "div",
          {
            "className": "card "
          },
          [
            "header",
            {},
            [
              "span",
              {
                "className": "greek-text"
              },
              "ποιος, ποια, ποιο"
            ],
            [
              "h3",
              {},
              "Who / Which"
            ]
          ],
          [
            "div",
            {
              "className": "content"
            },
            [
              "p",
              {},
              "Used to ask about identity. It declines like an\n                        adjective."
            ],
            [
              "div",
              {
                "className": "example mt-4"
              },
              [
                "span",
                {
                  "className": "greek-text"
                },
                [
                  "strong",
                  {},
                  "Ποιος"
                ],
                " ",
                "είναι στην πόρτα;"
              ],
              " ",
              [
                "span",
                {
                  "className": "translation"
                },
                [
                  "strong",
                  {},
                  "Who"
                ],
                " ",
                "is at the door?"
              ]
            ]
          ]
        ],
        [
          "div",
          {
            "className": "card "
          },
          [
            "header",
            {},
            [
              "span",
              {
                "className": "greek-text"
              },
              "πόσος, πόση, πόσο"
            ],
            [
              "h3",
              {},
              "How much / many"
            ]
          ],
          [
            "div",
            {
              "className": "content"
            },
            [
              "p",
              {},
              "Used to ask about quantity."
            ],
            [
              "div",
              {
                "className": "example mt-4"
              },
              [
                "span",
                {
                  "className": "greek-text"
                },
                [
                  "strong",
                  {},
                  "Πόσο"
                ],
                " ",
                "κάνει;"
              ],
              " ",
              [
                "span",
                {
                  "className": "translation"
                },
                [
                  "strong",
                  {},
                  "How much"
                ],
                " ",
                "does it cost?"
              ]
            ]
          ]
        ],
        [
          "div",
          {
            "className": "card  Ti"
          },
          [
            "header",
            {},
            [
              "span",
              {
                "className": "greek-text"
              },
              "τι"
            ],
            [
              "h3",
              {},
              "What"
            ]
          ],
          [
            "div",
            {
              "className": "content"
            },
            [
              "p",
              {},
              "The universal \"what\". It is indeclinable (stays the\n                        same)."
            ],
            [
              "div",
              {
                "className": "example mt-4"
              },
              [
                "span",
                {
                  "className": "greek-text"
                },
                [
                  "strong",
                  {},
                  "Τι"
                ],
                " ",
                "κάνεις;"
              ],
              " ",
              [
                "span",
                {
                  "className": "translation"
                },
                [
                  "strong",
                  {},
                  "What"
                ],
                " ",
                "are you doing?"
              ]
            ]
          ]
